tnam%2Famp_articleshow%2F112212304.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fnri%2Fother-news%2Findian-man-suffers-excruciating-pain-after-live-2-foot-eel-bites-through-intestines-in-vietnam%2Famp_articleshow%2F112212304.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Death%20Awaited%20Hamas%20Chief%20For%202%20Months%20In%20A%20Posh%20Tehran%20Locality%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDeath%20waited%20for%20Hamas%20chief%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20for%20over%20two%20months.%20A%20bomb%20was%20secretly%20smuggled%20into%20the%20guesthouse%20in%20Iran%20where%20he%20was%20expected%20to%20arrive%2C%20reports%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20citing%20several%20officials%20in%20the%20US%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hidden%20in%20the%20guesthouse%20in%20a%20posh%20locality%20in%20Tehran%2C%20protected%20by%20the%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20Corps%20(IRGC)%20-%20around%20two%20months%20ago.%20The%20guesthouse%20was%20inside%20a%20large%20compound%20used%20by%20the%20IRGC%20for%20their%20secret%20meetings%20and%20housing%20important%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wait%2C%20though%2C%20was%20long%2C%20it%20was%20fruitful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaniyeh%2C%20a%20top%20Hamas%20negotiator%20who%20had%20led%20its%20political%20delegation%20in%20Qatar%2C%20arrived%20in%20Tehran%20to%20attend%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20of%20Iran's%20president%20Masoud%20Pezeshkian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20it%20was%20confirmed%20that%20he%20was%20in%20his%20room%20in%20the%20guesthouse%20and%20the%20assassins%20detonated%20the%20bomb%20remotely%2C%20reported%20NYT.%20The%20blast%20shook%20the%20building.%20A%20portion%20of%20the%20wall%20collapsed.%20Windows%20were%20shattered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaniyeh%20and%20a%20bodyguard%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20attack%20that%20Hamas%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Btreacherous%20Zionist%20raid%20on%20his%20residence%20in%20Tehran%26quot%3B.%20The%20Palestinian%20group%20engaged%20in%20a%20deadly%20fight%20over%20Israel's%20Gaza%20campaign%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bgrave%20escalation%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20accused%20Israel%20of%20the%20assassination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hamas%20chief's%20killing%20threatened%20to%20disrupt%20talks%20to%20end%20the%20war%20and%20unleash%20another%20wave%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20hasn't%20claimed%20responsibility%20yet.%20However%2C%20the%20report%20states%20that%20Israeli%20intelligence%20officials%20had%20shared%20details%20about%20the%20covert%20operation%20with%20Western%20officials%20in%20the%20immediate%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20US%20diplomat%20Antony%20Blinken%20had%20denied%20that%20the%20US%20had%20prior%20knowledge%20about%20the%20assassination%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20speculated%20earlier%20that%20Haniyeh%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20missile%20strike%2C%20but%20the%20missile%20theory%20raised%20doubts%20over%20how%20Israel%20evaded%20the%20air%20defence%20systems%20in%20the%20Iranian%20capital.%20The%20damage%20caused%20was%20minimal%2C%20much%20less%20than%20what%20a%20missile%20strike%20would%20have%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20found%20the%20assassins%20were%20able%20to%20find%20a%20gap%20in%20Iranian%20security%20to%20smuggle%20in%20the%20bomb%2C%20though%20it%20remains%20unclear%20how%20they%20managed%20to%20keep%20it%20hidden%20for%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20rumours%20of%20witnesses%20seeing%20a%20missile-like%20object%20hitting%20the%20window%20of%20Haniyeh's%20room%2C%20but%20Iranian%20officials%20have%20confirmed%20that%20the%20blast%20occurred%20inside%20the%20room%20and%20that%20the%20bomb%20had%20been%20placed%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Middle%20Eastern%20officials%2C%20it%20took%20months%20for%20the%20planning%20and%20needed%20detailed%20surveillance%20of%20the%20compound.%20The%20planning%20was%20so%20precise%20that%20the%20next%20room%2C%20where%20Palestinian%20Islamic%20Jihad%20leader%20Ziyad%20al-Nakhalah%20was%20staying%2C%20wasn't%20as%20badly%20damaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assassination%20has%20caused%20tremendous%20embarrassment%20for%20Iranian%20officials%20who%20are%20yet%20to%20find%20out%20how%20or%20when%20the%20bombs%20were%20planted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20medical%20team%20housed%20in%20the%20compound%20declared%20Haniyeh%20dead.%20They%20failed%20to%20revive%20the%20bodyguard%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20spy%20and%20foreign%20intelligence%20agency%20Mossad%20is%20primarily%20tasked%20with%20assassinations%20outside%20the%20country.%20Mossad%20chief%20David%20Barnea%20had%20vowed%20to%20hunt%20down%20Hamas%20leaders%20after%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20said%20it%20would%20take%20time%2C%20like%20it%20had%20after%20the%20Munich%20massacre%2C%20to%20get%20hold%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarnea%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20murder%20of%2011%20Israeli%20athletes%20by%20Palestinian%20operatives%20at%20the%201972%20Olympics%20in%20Munich.%20Mossad%20had%20activated%20its%20hit%20squad%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20'Operation%20Wrath%20of%20God'%20covert%20operation%2C%20codenamed%20Bayonet%2C%20to%20avenge%20the%20murders.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722573360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fun7jfe78_ismail-haniyeh-_625x300_01_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdeath-waited-for-hamas-chief-for-2-months-in-a-posh-tehran-locality-6244629%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Death%20waited%20for%20Hamas%20chief%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20for%20over%20two%20months.%20A%20bomb%20was%20secretly%20smuggled%20into%20the%20guesthouse%20in%20Iran%20where%20he%20was%20expected%20to%20arrive%2C%20reports%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20citing%20several%20officials%20in%20the%20US%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworl