our%20Microgreens%20Using%20This%20Portable%2C%20Chemical-Free%20Cultivator%20Made%20of%20Banana%20Pulp%20Waste%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Snehal%20Ambekar%20was%20just%2017%2C%20she%20faced%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295026%2Fhealthcare-startup-to-manage-pcos-for-indian-women-by-sisters-raises-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultitude%20of%20health%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20felt%20dizzy%20when%20she%20stood%20up%2C%20had%20blackouts%2C%20brain%20fog%2C%20sleep%20arthritis%2C%20and%20an%20overwhelming%20sense%20of%20fatigue.%20Things%20were%20so%20bad%20that%20this%20young%20girl%20was%20bedridden.%20She%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20focus%20on%20her%20studies%20or%20even%20step%20out%20of%20the%20house.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20during%20the%20advent%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20since%20some%20of%20her%20symptoms%20matched%20with%20COVID-19%2C%20her%20parents%20had%20her%20tested%20for%20it.%20When%20she%20tested%20negative%2C%20the%20doctor%20suggested%20a%20complete%20blood%20checkup%20with%20tests%20%E2%80%94%20including%20thyroid%2C%20diabetes%2C%20iron%2C%20serum%20creatinine%2C%20Vitamin%20B12%2C%20D%2C%20B9%2C%20etc.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20some%20X-rays%20and%20the%20result%20was%20clear%3A%20Snehal%20was%20nutritionally%20deficient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teenager%20was%20shocked.%20%E2%80%9CI%20ate%20home-cooked%20vegetarian%20meals%20and%20followed%20a%20healthy%20diet.%20I%20was%20young%2C%20healthy%2C%20and%20exercised%20regularly.%20How%20could%20I%20have%20a%20vitamin%20deficiency%3F%20I%20was%20in%20disbelief%2C%E2%80%9D%20Snehal%20(22)%20recalls%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20diagnosis%20shed%20light%20on%20an%20often-overlooked%20aspect%20of%20nutrition%3A%20the%20potential%20for%20deficiency%20even%20in%20seemingly%20healthy%20diets.%20Moreover%2C%20her%20condition%20was%20compounded%20by%20a%20diagnosis%20of%20Polycystic%20Ovary%20Syndrome%20(PCOS)%2C%20a%20hormonal%20disorder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20popping%20more%20than%2010%20pills%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20Mumbai%20resident%2C%20who%20was%20then%20given%20a%20battery%20of%20medicines%20for%20different%20vitamin%20deficiencies%20and%20advised%20a%20complete%20overhaul%20in%20her%20diet%2C%20exercise%2C%20and%20overall%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20she%20buried%20herself%20in%20research%20to%20understand%20which%20foods%20were%20nutrient-dense%20and%20aid%20in%20a%20healthy%20life.%20One%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98superfoods%E2%80%99%20she%20found%20at%20this%20time%20was%20microgreens.%20Little%20did%20she%20realise%20then%20that%20she%20would%20be%20launching%20an%20associated%20startup%20with%20her%20classmate%2C%20Sayak%20Gupta%2C%20four%20years%20later!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Snehal%20and%20Sayak%2C%20Founders%20of%20SS%20Agriqulture%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359444%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESnehal%20and%20Sayak%2C%20Founders%20of%20SS%20Agriqulture%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Snehal%20and%20Sayak%2C%20two%20food%20technologists%2C%20devised%20a%20portable%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349300%2Fhow-to-grow-microgreens-at-home-or-farm-aditi-mali-of-mali-greens-shares-tips%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoilless%20microgreens%20cultivator%20%3C%2Fa%3Elabelled%20%E2%80%98Half%20Inch%20Garden%E2%80%99%20through%20their%20venture%20SS%20AgriQulture%20Innovations.%20What%20sets%20this%20cultivator%20apart%20is%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20require%20any%20seeds.%20Instead%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20seed%20patches%20made%20from%20agricultural%20waste%2C%20such%20as%20banana%20pulp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20friends%20are%20now%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20make%20growing%20superfoods%20convenient%20and%20accessible%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20garden%20that%20fits%20on%20your%20coffee%20table!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20friends%20met%20while%20pursuing%20a%20BTech%20(Bachelor%20of%20Technology)%20in%20food%20technology%2C%20entrepreneurship%20and%20management%20from%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Food%20Technology%2C%20Entrepreneurship%20and%20Management%20%E2%80%93%20Kundli%20(NIFTEM-K)%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-30-1722571725.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-30-1722571725.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-30-1722571725-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-30-1722571725-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-30-1722571725-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-30-1722571725-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359448%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayak%20(22)%20also%20had%20a%20deep%20passion%20for%20nutrition%20and%20wanted%20to%20develop%20a%20product%20that%20could%20make%20nutrition%20available%20to%20people%20in%20the%20comfort%20of%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTraditionally%2C%20India%20has%20only%20focused%20on%20protein%2C%20while%20missing%20out%20on%20micronutrients.%20Vitamins%2C%20minerals%2C%20and%20phytonutrients%20are%20equally%20important%20and%20beneficial%20to%20us.%20We%20generally%20rely%20on%20supplements%20and%20medicines%20to%20get%20these%20nutrients.%20But%20nothing%20beats%20real%20food%2C%20which%20gives%20you%20good%20results%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sayak%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20beetroot%20microgreens%2C%20which%20are%20only%20one%20to%20two%20inches%20in%20height%20and%20weigh%2030%20grams%2C%20will%20give%20you%20as%20many%20vitamins%20as%20half%20a%20kilogram%20of%20beetroot.%20These%20tiny%20plants%20pack%20a%20punch%2C%20literally%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayak%20says%20that%20microgreens%20contain%20significantly%20more%20nutrients%20than%20mature%20vegetables.%20To%20explain%20the%20benefits%20that%20microgreens%20offer%2C%20Dr%20Akshat%20Chadha%2C%20a%20general%20physician%20with%20expertise%20in%20lifestyle%20medicine%2C%20lists%20their%20advantages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20microgreens%20are%20rich%20in%20iron%2C%20Vitamin%20K%2C%20Vitamin%20C%2C%20selenium%2C%20magnesium%2C%20manganese%2C%20antioxidants%2C%20and%20Vitamin%20E.%20They%20are%20a%20good%20addition%20to%20the%20diet%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Chadha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F304873%2Fkerala-man-grows-microgreens-superfood-at-home-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20microgreens%20is%20not%20new%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20traditional%20methods%20are%20often%20cumbersome%2C%20as%20they%20consume%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20and%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESnehal%20(22)%20faced%20these%20challenges%20when%20she%20tried%20growing%20them%20at%20her%20house.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20usually%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20balconies%20to%20grow%20plants.%20They%20also%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20care%2C%20which%20becomes%20difficult%20in%20our%20hectic%20schedules.%20I%20failed%20in%20my%20experiments%20due%20to%20mould%20formation%20and%20wanted%20to%20find%20an%20easier%20way%20to%20grow%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESnehal%E2%80%99s%20personal%20experience%20combined%20with%20Sayak%E2%80%99s%20passion%20and%20their%20course%20knowledge%20led%20them%20to%20start%20working%20on%20an%20automated%20cultivator%20that%20helps%20%E2%80%9Cgrow%20your%20own%20vitamins%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%204032px)%20100vw%2C%204032px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-24-at-11.20.54-3-min-1722571731.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20automated%20microgreens%20cultivator%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-24-at-11.20.54-3-min-1722571731.jpeg%204032w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-24-at-11.20.54-3-min-1722571731-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-24-at-11.20.54-3-min-1722571731-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-24-at-11.20.54-3-min-1722571731-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-24-at-11.20.54-3-min-1722571731-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-24-at-11.20.54-3-min-1722571731-2048x1536.jpeg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-24-at-11.20.54-3-min-1722571731-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359449%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20automated%20microgreens%20cultivator%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20on%20the%20tech-to-table%20model%2C%20the%20duo%20started%20developing%20their%20idea%20in%20college%20itself.%20Their%20first%20win%20came%20at%20IIT%20Bombay%E2%80%99s%20business%20model%20competition%2C%20Eureka%2C%20in%20January%202023%2C%20where%20they%20won%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20With%20this%20prize%20money%2C%20they%20started%20working%20on%20the%20first%20prototype%20of%20their%20cultivator%2C%20the%20Half%20Inch%20Garden.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20garden%20that%20fits%20perfectly%20on%20your%20dining%20table%20or%20coffee%20table%E2%80%9D%2C%20says%20Sayak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20received%20over%20Rs%2018%20lakh%20in%20grants%20from%20various%20institutions%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20Massive%20Earth%20Foundation%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Environment%20Programme%20(UNEP)%2C%20IIT%20Roorkee%2C%20IIM%20Kashipur%2C%20and%20more.%20The%20startup%20is%20also%20recognised%20by%20the%20Department%20for%20Promotion%20of%20Industry%20and%20Internal%20Trade%20(DPIIT)%2C%20a%20central%20government%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20automated%2C%20handy%20cultivator%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F257325%2Fhow-to-grow-microgreens-fenugreek-mustard-recycle-milk-packets-workshops-organic-farming-vegetables-nutrition-sustainable-jaipur-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoilless%20unit%20and%20comes%20with%20seed%20patches.%3C%2Fa%3E%20These%20patches%20are%20thin%20sheets%20that%20come%20embedded%20with%20seeds.%20The%20sheets%20are%20made%20using%20biodegradable%20fibres%20and%20agricultural%20waste%20like%20banana%20fibre.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sheet%20itself%20acts%20as%20a%20growing%20medium%20for%20the%20microgreens%2C%20providing%20essential%20nutrients.%20There%20are%20no%20pesticides%20required.%20We%20have%20formulated%20and%20manufactured%20this%20sheet%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sayak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20uses%20a%20hydroponic%20technology%20and%20comes%20with%20a%20grow%20light%20that%20mimics%20the%20wavelength%20of%20the%20sun.%20It%20also%20has%20two%20exhaust%20fans%20inside%20to%20circulate%20the%20airflow%20and%20an%20automatic%20irrigation%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20one%20has%20to%20do%20after%20getting%20the%20machine%20is%20to%20fill%20the%20water%20container%20with%20two%20and%20a%20half%20litres%20of%20water.%20You%20can%20place%20four%20seed%20patches%20at%20a%20time%20in%20the%20slots%20provided.%20Switch%20it%20on%20and%20forget%20about%20it!%20After%20five%20to%20eight%20days%2C%20your%20harvest%20will%20be%20ready%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Snehal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sheets%20always%20have%20a%20particular%20amount%20of%20moisture%2C%20and%20water%20is%20transported%20to%20the%20sheets%20through%20a%20rope%20using%20capillary%20action%2C%20explains%20Sayak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20seven%20prototypes%2C%20the%20entrepreneurs%20have%20zeroed%20in%20on%20their%20final%20version%20and%20hope%20to%20start%20production%20soon.%20They%20have%20tested%20and%20validated%20eight%20varieties%20of%20microgreens%20%E2%80%94%20including%20beetroot%2C%20broccoli%2C%20green%20mustard%2C%20chia%2C%20clover%20and%20wheatgrass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20plan%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F249858%2Fhow-to-microgreens-coconut-shell-seetha-anand-vaidyam-hyderabad-wellness-coach-compost-vegetable-fruit-peel-cocopeat-information-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaunch%20the%20automated%20cultivator%20next%20month%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20keep%20it%20on%20a%20subscription%20basis.%20We%20would%20be%20providing%20four%20patches%20with%20the%20machine%2C%20post%20which%2C%20we%20would%20be%20selling%20patches%20separately%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Snehal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20motive%20is%20to%20make%20Indians%20include%20microgreens%20as%20part%20of%20their%20daily%20diet.%20%E2%80%9CEat%20your%20vitamins%20before%20you%20have%20to%20start%20taking%20supplements%2C%E2%80%9D%20Snehal%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Sayak%20Gupta%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722573085000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359436%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Food%20technologists%20Snehal%20Ambekar%20and%20Sayak%20Gupta%20have%20designed%20an%20automated%20cultivator%20for%20growing%20microgreens.%20Their%20venture%20SS%20Agriqulture%20Innovations%20is%20using%20the%20%E2%80%98Half-Inch%20Garden%E2%80%99%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20