ch%20Ops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBraving%20rains%20and%20adverse%20terrain%2C%2040%20teams%20of%20rescuers%20resumed%20search%20operations%20in%20landslide-hit%20Wayanad%20district%20on%20the%20fourth%20day%20on%20Friday%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20and%20rescue%20operations%20that%20got%20underway%20early%20morning%20received%20an%20impetus%20due%20to%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20190-foot-long%20Bailey%20bridge%20that%20will%20enable%20the%20movement%20of%20heavy%20machinery%2C%20including%20excavators%2C%20and%20ambulances%20to%20the%20worst-affected%20Mundakkai%20and%20Chooralmala%20hamlets%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Defence%20source%20said%20Columns%20with%20dog%20squads%20commenced%20search%20operations%20at%207%20am.%20Search%20operations%20were%20planned%20based%20on%20local%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2040%20teams%20will%20conduct%20search%20operations%20in%20six%20zones%20of%20the%20landslides-hit%20areas%20--%20Attamala%20and%20Aaranmala%20(first)%2C%20Mundakkai%20(second)%2C%20Punchirimattam%20(third)%2C%20Vellarimala%20village%20(fourth)%2C%20GVHSS%20Vellarimala%20(fifth)%2C%20and%20riverbank%20(sixth).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20teams%20will%20include%20personnel%20from%20the%20army%2C%20NDRF%2C%20DSG%2C%20Coast%20Guard%2C%20Navy%2C%20and%20MEG%20along%20with%20three%20locals%20and%20one%20forest%20department%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20a%20three-pronged%20search%20operation%20will%20begin%2C%20focusing%20on%20the%20Chaliyar%20River%2C%20according%20to%20the%20rescue%20plan%20devised%20by%20the%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eight%20police%20stations%2C%20along%20the%2040-km%20stretch%20of%20Chaliyar%2C%20will%20join%20forces%20with%20local%20swimming%20experts%20to%20search%20the%20river%20for%20bodies%20that%20may%20have%20flown%20downstream%20or%20are%20trapped%20along%20the%20riverbanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimultaneously%2C%20another%20search%20operation%20will%20be%20conducted%20using%20a%20police%20helicopter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20this%2C%20the%20Coast%20Guard%2C%20Navy%2C%20and%20Forest%20Department%20will%20jointly%20conduct%20a%20search%20operation%20focusing%20on%20the%20riverbanks%20and%20areas%20where%20bodies%20may%20be%20trapped%2C%20according%20to%20the%20rescue%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20sources%2C%20the%20extent%20of%20human%20loss%20will%20emerge%20when%20rescuers%20clear%20houses%20covered%20by%20debris%20and%20wood%20logs%20using%20heavy%20machinery.%20So%20far%2C%20295%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20and%20over%20200%20missing%20in%20the%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Revenue%20Minister%20K%20Rajan%2C%20a%20day%20ago%2C%20had%20said%20that%20a%20drone-based%20radar%20from%20Delhi%20would%20arrive%20on%20Saturday%20to%20locate%20bodies%20buried%20in%20the%20mud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20currently%2C%20six%20dogs%20are%20assisting%20in%20the%20search%20operation%20and%20four%20more%20will%20arrive%20in%20Wayanad%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722572880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fk88e4l8o_wayanad-landslide_625x300_02_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwayanad-landslides-295-dead-in-kerala-landslides-40-rescue-teams-resume-search-ops-6245002%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Braving%20rains%20and%20adverse%20terrain%2C%2040%20teams%20of%20rescuers%20resumed%20search%20operations%20in%20landslide-hit%20Wayanad%20district%20on%20the%20fourth%20day%20on%20Friday%2C%20officials%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwayanad-landslides-295-dead-in-kerala-lan