20exam.%20The%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20clutch%20of%20petitions%20demanding%20the%20NEET-UG%20test%20-%20a%20qualifying%20examination%20for%20undergraduate%20medical%20courses%20-%20be%20either%20held%20again%20or%20cancelled.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20after%20an%20unusually%20high%20number%20of%20students%20scored%20a%20perfect%20720%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%20exam.%20Red%20flags%20were%20raised%20over%20the%20number%20-%2067%20-%20of%20perfect%20scores%2C%20including%20a%20coaching%20centre%20in%20Haryana's%20Bahadurgarh%20that%20produced%20six%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInitially%20attributed%20to%20grace%20marks%20due%20to%20a%20faulty%20question%20and%20logistical%20issues%2C%20subsequent%20investigations%20by%20Police%20uncovered%20a%20different%20aspect%3A%20the%20exam%20paper%20had%20been%20leaked%20to%20select%20candidates%20a%20day%20before%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOne%20of%20the%20questions%20in%20the%20Physics%20paper%20had%20multiple%20correct%20answers%2C%20and%20hence%20all%20students%20had%20been%20awarded%20full%20marks%20for%20that%20question%2C%20the%20testing%20agency%20NTA%20had%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20roped%20in%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Delhi%20to%20ascertain%20if%20there%20were%20indeed%20multiple%20answers%20to%20the%20question.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20panel%20of%20three%20experts%20confirmed%20there%20was%20only%20one%20correct%20answer%20to%20the%20question%20and%20that%20the%20answer%20was%20the%20same%20as%20provided%20in%20the%20answer%20key%20initially%20issued%20by%20the%20NTA.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20hearing%20all%20sides%2C%20the%20court%20on%20July%2023%20ruled%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20re-test%20for%20the%20NEET%20exam%20as%20there%20is%20no%20data%20to%20suggest%20a%20%26quot%3Bsystemic%20breach%26quot%3B%20or%20the%20%26quot%3Bsanctity%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20examination.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20court%20had%20said%20that%20