and%20relief%20work%20to%20evacuate%20the%20people%20stranded%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Uttarakhand%20police%2C%20as%20many%20as%20737%20people%20were%20rescued%20by%20helicopter%20and%20at%20least%202%2C670%20people%20were%20taken%20to%20Sonprayag%20by%20the%20relief%20forces%20as%20of%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20to%20its%20official%20handle%20on%20X%2C%20Uttarakhand%20police%20posted%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20rescue%20work%20of%20people%20stranded%20on%20the%20Shri%20Kedarnath%20Dham%20Yatra%20route%20is%20continuing.%20737%20passengers%20were%20rescued%20by%20helicopter%20throughout%20the%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B2%2C670%20passengers%20were%20taken%20to%20Sonprayag.%20SDRF%2C%20NDRF%2C%20DDRF%2C%20District%20Police%20and%20Administration%20teams%20are%20selflessly%20helping%20the%20devotees%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Abhinav%20Kumar%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20gave%20information%20about%20the%20relief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20after%20heavy%20rains%20in%20the%20state%20and%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20and%20travellers%20to%20be%20cautious%20and%20follow%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20heavy%20rainfall%20in%20Tehri%20and%20Rudraprayag%20districts%2C%20Uttarakhand%20DGP%20Abhinav%20Kumar%20informed%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20Kedarnath%20Yatra%20has%20been%20suspended%20for%20two%20days%20due%20to%20weather%20conditions%20and%2012%20NDRF%20as%20well%20as%2060%20SDRF%20teams%20are%20engaged%20in%20rescue%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%20on%20the%20situation%20created%20by%20heavy%20rains%20in%20Tehri%20and%20Rudraprayag%20districts%2C%20Uttarakhand%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20Abhinav%20Kumar%20said%20on%20Thursday%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20received%20an%20alert%20from%20the%20Meteorological%20Department%20about%20heavy%20rains%20in%20the%