century%2C%20a%20new%20'Chakravyuh'%20has%20been%20formed%20-%20that%20too%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20Lotus.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20wears%20its%20symbol%20on%20his%20chest.%20What%20was%20done%20with%20Abhimanyu%2C%20is%20being%20down%20with%20India%20-%20the%20youth%2C%20farmers%2C%20women%2C%20small%20and%20medium%20businesses.%20Abhimanyu%20was%20killed%20by%20six%20people.%20Today%2C%20too%20there%20are%20six%20people%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20'Chakravyuh'.%20Six%20people%20control%20India%20today%20too%20-Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%2C%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20Ambani%20and%20Adani%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LoP%20said%20that%20the%20budget%20has%20stabbed%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20which%20enthusiastically%20banged%20thalis%20when%20asked%20to%20do%20so%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LoP%20said%20that%20the%20'Chakravyuh'%20that%20the%20central%20government%20has%20built%20is%20harming%20crores%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Anurag%20Thakur%20took%20a%20jibe%20at%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20statements%20on%20Mahabharata%20and%20Chakravyuh%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20said%20that%20some%20people%20are%20'accidental%20Hindus'%20and%20their%20knowledge%20of%20Mahabharata%20is%20accidental%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnurag%20Thakur%20attacked%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Chakravyuh%20statement%20and%20said%20that%20he%20did%20well%20by%20raising%20the%20topic%20of%20Chakravyuh%20because%20this%20country%20has%20well%20seen%20many%20%26quot%3BChakravyuhs%20of%20Congress%20Party.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20attacked%20Congress%20by%20counting%207%20Chakravyuhs%20while%20saying%20that%20the%20first%20Chakravyuh%20was%20Congress%20itself%2C%20which%20divided%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20applauded%20BJP%20leader%20Anurag%20Thakur%20for%20his%20speech%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20w