u%20even%20dictated%20a%20few%20points%20but%20had%20no%20answer%20to%20Bing%20Jiao's%20superior%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20should%20have%20controlled%20in%20terms%20of%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20mistakes%20on%20my%20defense%20is%20what%20I%20felt%2C%26quot%3B%20Sindhu%20said%2C%20reflecting%20upon%20the%20reason%20for%20her%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESindhu%20had%20a%20training%20camp%20in%20Germany%20and%20also%20joined%20forces%20with%20mentor%20Prakash%20Padukone%20for%20better%20preparation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20worked%20hard%2C%20so%20we've%20done%20whatever%20we%20could.%20Rest%20is%20destiny.%20I%20don't%20regret%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20kept%20fighting%20still%20because%20you%20never%20know%20anything%20can%20happen.%20Both%20of%20us%20were%20fighting%20for%20each%20point%20because%20until%20the%20end%20you%20can't%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20easy%20win%20or%20easy%20points%2C%20you%20can't%20think%20that%20you%20have%20finished%20the%20game.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBing%20Jiao's%20smashes%20and%20soft%20drops%20had%20Sindhu%20scurrying%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20court.%20But%20when%20Sindhu%20attacked%2C%20the%20Chinese%20defended%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20has%20that%20jump%20smash.%20Even%20my%20smashes%2C%20I%20think%2C%20which%20were%20mid-court%2C%20they%20were%20just%20going%20out%20when%20she%20was%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20should%20have%20hit%20them%20inside%20and%20I%20should%20have%20got%20those%20points%20where%20I've%20made%20those%20unforced%20errors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20got%20much%20more%20confident%20in%20that%20because%20when%20I%20was%20hitting%2C%20she%20was%20defending%2C%20but%20still%20some%20points%20which%20were%20really%20mid-court%20also%2C%20I%20was%20hitting%20just%20out%20or%20just%20into%20her%20hand.%26quot%3B%20It%20was%20neck-and-neck%20in%20the%20first%20game%20with%20Sindhu%20and%20her%20rival%20locked%2019-19.%20The%20two-time%20Olympic%20medalist%20said%20winning%20the%20game%20from%20that%20position%20could%20have%20changed%20things%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20sad%20that%20I%20couldn't%20convert%20it%20to%20win%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20first%20game%20because%20it%20was%2019%20all%20at%20some%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20if%20it%20would%20have%20been%20the%20other%20way%2C%20especially%20when%20I%20challenged%20it.%20If%20I%20would%20have%20won%20the%20first%20set%2C%20maybe%20it%20would%20have%20been%20different.%20But%20I%20think%20it%20was...%20I%20mean%2C%20there%20were%20rallies%20and%20it%20was%20going%20on%20well%2C%20but%20only%20one%20can%20win.%26quot%3B%20Asked%20if%20she%20would%20try%20to%20play%20in%20the%20next%20Olympics%20in%20the%20USA%2C%20Sindhu%20was%20non-committal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20still%20four%20years%20away.%20So%20for%20me%2C%20right%20now%2C%20I%20just%20go%20back%20and%20rest%20for%20a%20bit%2C%20maybe%20just%20take%20some%20break%20and%20then%20come%20back%20and%20let's%20see%20what%20it%20is%20because%20four%20years%20is%20a%20very%2C%20very%20long%20time.%20So%20let's%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2029-year-old%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20sad.%20The%20result%2C%20I%20couldn't%20get%20what%20I%20expected%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20journey%2C%20isn't%20it%3F%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20a%20wonderful%20journey%20so%20far.%20There%20were%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%20and%20I%20came%20back%20from%20an%20injury%2C%20and%20everything%20was%20going%20on%20well.%20You%20can't%20expect%20easy%20wins%20or%20picking%20the%20form%20at%20the%20right%20time.%20Sometimes%20it%20might%20not%20be%20your%20day.%20We%20all%20really%20worked%20hard.%26quot%3B%20In%20game%20two%2C%20Sindhu%20tried%20to%20unsettle%20Bing%20Jiao%20with%20smashes%20but%20her%20opponent%20was%20picking%20up%20all%20those%20low%20shots%20as%20well.%3C