er%20David%20Zinsner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20implementing%20our%20spending%20reductions%2C%20we%20are%20taking%20proactive%20steps%20to%20improve%20our%20profits%20and%20strengthen%20our%20balance%20sheet%2C%26quot%3B%20Zinsner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntel%20reported%20having%20124%2C800%20employees%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%2C%20meaning%20the%20layoffs%20could%20hit%20about%2018%2C000%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20Intel%20announced%20it%20was%20halting%20the%20expansion%20of%20a%20major%20factory%20project%20in%20Israel%2C%20which%20was%20going%20to%20pump%20an%20extra%20%2415%20billion%20towards%20a%20chip%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntel%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20%26quot%3Bmanaging%20large-scale%20projects%2C%20especially%20in%20our%20industry%2C%20often%20involves%20adapting%20to%20changing%20timelines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDecisions%20are%20based%20on%20business%20conditions%2C%20market%20dynamics%20and%20responsible%20capital%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20US-based%20company%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20belt-tightening%20came%20just%20a%20month%20after%20Intel%20struck%20a%20defiant%20tone%20in%20the%20face%20of%20strong%20challenges%20from%20rivals%20Nvidia%2C%20AMD%20and%20Qualcomm%2C%20unveiling%20technologies%20it%20said%20would%20lead%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20Intel%20has%20dominated%20the%20market%20for%20the%20chips%20that%20run%20everything%20from%20laptops%20to%20data%20centres.%20But%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20its%20competitors%20--%20especially%20Nvidia%20--%20have%20soared%20ahead%20on%20specialized%20AI%20processors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20keynote%20speech%20at%20Taiwan's%20Computex%20expo%2C%20Gelsinger%20introduced%20Intel's%20latest%20Xeon%206%20processors%20for%20servers%2C%20and%20shared%20more%20details%20about%20its%20next-gen%20Lunar%20Lake%20chips%20for%20AI%20PCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20driving%20one%20of%20the%20most%20consequential%20eras%20of%20innovation%20the%20industry%20has%20ever%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20Gelsinger%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20magic%20of%20silicon%20is%20once%20again%20enabling%20exponential%20advancements%20in%20computing%20that%20will%20push%20the%20boundaries%20of%20human%20potential%20and%20power%20the%20global%20economy%20for%20years%20to%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGelsinger%20said%20Intel's%20latest%20equipment%20provides%20the%20best%20available%20mix%20of%20performance%2C%20energy%20efficiency%20and%20affordability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20presentation%20followed%20earlier%20keynote%20speeches%20by%20Nvidia%20boss%20Jensen%20Huang%2C%20AMD%20CEO%20Lisa%20Su%20and%20Qualcomm's%20Cristiano%20Amon%20--%20and%20they%20were%20replete%20with%20claims%20and%20counterclaims%20about%20which%20firm's%20products%20were%20the%20best%20for%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20in%20June%20unveiled%20its%20Copilot%2B%20AI%20PCs%2C%20which%20will%20have%20artificial%20intelligence%20features%20built%20into%20its%20Windows%20operating%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20Microsoft%2C%20the%20features%20will%20be%20added%20by%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20computer%20manufacturers%2C%20including%20Dell%2C%20HP%2C%20Samsung%20and%20Lenovo%2C%20offering%20AI%20capabilities%20on%20the%20device%20itself%2C%20not%20just%20through%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20computers%20are%20expected%20to%20be%2080%20percent%20of%20the%20PC%20market%20by%202028%2C%20Intel%20said%2C%20citing%20the%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722560040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2Fhl4hnpm4_intel_625x300_29_June_22.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22http