ter%2C%20Kumar%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20rescue%20operation%20was%20initiated%20and%20the%20rainwater%20was%20pumped%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20were%20recovered%20by%20the%20SDRF%20during%20a%20rescue%20operation%20that%20lasted%20several%20hours%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20condolences%20over%20the%20incident%2C%20CM%20Sharma%20directed%20officials%20to%20provide%20financial%20assistance%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20to%20the%20family%20of%20each%20deceased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproval%20to%20grant%20Rs%204%20lakh%20from%20disaster%20relief%20fund%20and%20Rs%201%20lakh%20from%20chief%20minister's%20relief%20fund%20has%20been%20given%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20CM%20Diya%20Kumari%20visited%20the%20family%20members%20of%20the%20deceased%20and%20expressed%20condolences.%20She%20said%20that%20efforts%20have%20been%20made%20to%20address%20the%20problem%20of%20water%20logging%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20area%20have%20been%20advised%20not%20to%20stay%20in%20their%20basements%20during%20rainfall%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20of%20the%20victims%20have%20been%20shifted%20to%20Kanwatiya%20Government%20Hospital%20for%20postmortem%2C%20the%20police%20said%2C%20all%20the%20victims%20are%20native%20of%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20were%20handed%20over%20after%20postmortem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jhalawar%2C%20three%20people%2C%20including%20a%20woman%2C%20riding%20on%20a%20motorcycle%20on%20a%20bridge%20were%20swept%20away%20by%20the%20overflowing%20Kalisindh%20river%20this%20afternoon%2C%20Mandawar%20SHO%20Mahaveer%20Prasad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20not%20been%20identified%20yet%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20search%20operation%20was%20launched%20but%20none%20of%20them%20could%20be%20traced%20till%20the%20evening%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jaipur's%20Bagru%2