mentary%20chargesheet%20as%20the%20investigations%20are%20in%20an%20advanced%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20and%20Amit%20Anand%20are%20the%20two%20kingpins%20while%20the%20four%20candidates%20who%20feature%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20are%20Ayush%20Kumar%2C%20Anurag%20Yadav%2C%20Abhishek%20Kumar%2C%20and%20Shivnandan%20Kumar.%20Sikander%20Yadvendu%2C%20a%20junior%20engineer%20from%20Bihar's%20Danapur%20Town%20Council%2C%20is%20also%20named%20in%20the%20document.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%2013%20accused%2C%20including%20the%20four%20examinees%2C%20were%20booked%20under%20sections%20dealing%20with%20criminal%20breach%20of%20trust%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20its%20investigation%20so%20far%2C%20the%20CBI%20believes%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Patna's%20Gopalpur%2C%20is%20the%20main%20accused%20and%20allegedly%20one%20of%20four%20%26quot%3Bsetters%26quot%3B.%20He%2C%20along%20with%20Amit%20Anand%20and%20Sikander%20Yadvendu%2C%20hatched%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20leak%20the%20paper%20for%20a%20price%20of%20Rs%2030-32%20lakh%20per%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20also%20revealed%20that%20Yadvendu%20had%20told%20Kumar%20and%20Anand%20that%20he%20had%20four%20students%20who%20were%20ready%20to%20buy%20papers.%20%26quot%3BFour%20students%20were%20called%20by%20Amit%20on%20the%20night%20of%20May%204%20(the%20eve%20of%20the%20exam)%20and%20made%20to%20solve%20the%20leaked%20question%20paper%20and%20memorise%20answers%2C%26quot%3B%20states%20the%20chargesheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20said%20the%20CBI%20utilised%20advanced%20forensic%20techniques%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20CCTV%20footage%20and%20location%20analysis%2C%20among%20others%2C%20to%20gather%20evidence%20against%20the%20accused%2C%20which%20has%20been%20presented%20before%20the%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CBI%20is%20continuing%20further%20investigation%20against%20other%20accused%2Fsuspects%20and%20on%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20case.%20Several%20other%20accused%20are%20already%20in%20custody.%20When%20the%20investigation%20against%20the%20other%20people%20is%20complete%2C%20one%20or%20more%20supplementary%20chargesheets%20will%20be%20filed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20central%20agency%20has%20arrested%2040%20people%20in%20this%20case%20-%20including%2015%20who%20were%20arrested%20by%20Bihar%20Police%20-%20and%20conducted%20searches%20at%2058%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20Accused%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENitish%20Kumar%20had%20been%20jailed%20earlier%20this%20year%20as%20well%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20paper%20leak%20in%20a%20Bihar%20Public%20Services%20(BPSC)%20examination.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAmit%20Anand%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Mangal%20Bazar%20in%20Munger%2C%20has%20told%20the%20CBI%20that%20the%20question%20paper%20was%20leaked%20on%20May%204%2C%20a%20day%20before%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAshutosh%20Kumar%2C%20a%20Jamui%20resident%20living%20in%20Rajiv%20Nagar%2C%20Patna%2C%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20an%20associate%20of%20%26quot%3Bsetter%26quot%3B%20Amit%20Anand.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERoshan%20Kumar%2C%2035%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Ekangarsarai%2C%20Nalanda%2C%20also%20lives%20in%20Rajiv%20Nagar%20and%20is%20an%20associate%20of%20Amit%20Anand.%20His%20role%20was%20allegedly%20to%20convince%20candidates%20to%20buy%20the%20question%20paper.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAnurag%20Yadav%20from%20Danapur%2C%20Patna%2C%20allegedly%20approached%20the%20%26quot%3Bsetters%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESix%20Cases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20case%20into%20the%20alleged%20NEET-UG%20irregularities%20was%20registered%20by%20the%20Patna%20Police%20on%20May%205%20and%20later%20transferred%20to%20CBI%20on%20June%2023.%20The%20agency%20filed%20its%20first%20chargesheet%20in%2038%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20registered%20six%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIRs).%20The%20FIR%20from%20Bihar%20is%20on%20the%20paper%20leaks%20while%20the%20remaining%20ones%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Maharashtra%20are%20regarding%20impersonation%20of%20candidates%20and%20cheating.%20Another%2C%20filed%20on%20a%20reference%20from%20the%20Union%20education%20ministry%2C%20pertains%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensive%20investigation%26quot%3B%20into%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEET-UG%20is%20conducted%20by%20the%20NTA%20for%20admissions%20to%20MBBS%2C%20BDS%2C%20AYUSH%20and%20other%20related%20courses%20in%20government%20and%20private%20institutions.%20The%20exam%20was%20held%20across%20India%20on%20May%205%20and%20over%2023%20lakh%20students%20had%20appeared%20for%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllegations%20of%20paper%20leaks%20and%20arbitrary%20grace%20marks%20to%20over%201%2C500%20students%20triggered%20protests%2C%20and%20the%20opposition%20has%20also%20been%20attacking%20the%20government%20over%20the%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722534420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F8kin8q6g_entrance-exam-generic_625x300_14_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcandidates-parents-kingpins-named-in-cbis-1st-neet-chargesheet-6242838%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Filing%20its%20first%20chargesheet%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%20paper%20leak%20case%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20has%20named%2013%20people%2C%20including%20four%20candidates%2C%20a%20junior%20engineer%20and%20two%20kingpins.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcandidates-parents-kingpins-named-in-cbis-1st-neet-chargesheet-6242838%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2F