tml%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20regulator%20cited%20violations%20of%20norms%20related%20to%20policyholders'%20interests%2C%20web%20aggregators%2C%20and%20insurance%20distributors%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Firdai-levies-rs-2-cr-penalty-on-hdfc-life-insurance-for-violating-norms-124080101606_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Firdai-levies-rs-2-cr-penalty-on-hdfc-life-insurance-for-violating-norms-124080101606_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Firdai-levies-rs-2-cr-penalty-on-hdfc-life-insurance-for-violating-norms-124080101606_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRelationship%20Gone%20Sour%26quot%3B%3A%20High%20Court%20Cancels%20Rape%20Case%20Against%2073-Year-Old%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20quashed%20a%20case%20lodged%20against%20a%2073-year-old%20man%20for%20allegedly%20sexually%20abusing%20a%20woman%20since%201987%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20relationship%20was%20consensual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20A%20S%20Gadkari%20and%20Neela%20Gokhale%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20FIR%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20indicate%20a%20consensual%20relationship%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20noted%20the%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20in%202018%20and%20there%20has%20been%20no%20explanation%20for%20the%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20parties%20were%20indulging%20in%20sexual%20relationship%20for%20as%20many%20as%2031%20years.%20The%20complainant%20has%20never%20breathed%20a%20word%20about%20her%20alleged%20objection%20to%20the%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20classic%20case%20of%20a%20relationship%20between%20the%20parties%20turning%20sour%20and%20thereafter%20the%20complainant%20lodging%20a%20police%20complaint%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20case%2C%20the%20woman%20had%20joined%20the%20man's%20company%20in%201987.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20accused%20allegedly%20forcibly%20established%20sexual%20relations%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20between%20July%201987%20and%202017%2C%20for%2030%20years%2C%20the%20accused%20raped%20her%20at%20various%20hotels%20in%20Kalyan%2C%20Bhiwandi%20and%20other%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20case%2C%20he%20promised%20to%20marry%20her%2C%20put%20a%20%3Cem%3E'mangalsutra'%3C%2Fem%3E%20around%20her%20neck%20in%201993%20and%20declared%20she%20was%20his%20second%20wife.%20adding%20he%20did%20not%20permit%20her%20to%20marry%20anyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claimed%20that%20in%201996%20the%20accused%20suffered%20a%20heart%20attack%20so%20she%20looked%20after%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20September%202017%2C%20her%20mother%20suffered%20from%20cancer%20and%20she%20had%20to%20take%20a%20leave%20of%20absence%20from%20her%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20resumed%20service%2C%20she%20found%20the%20office%20closed%20and%20the%20company%20gate%20locked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20man%20once%20again%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20marry%20her%20and%20also%20did%20not%20hand%20over%20documents%20relating%20to%20banking%2C%20income%20tax%2C%20an%20agreement%20related%20to%20a%20medical%20shop%20and%20the%20gold%20'mangalsutra'.%20He%20also%20refused%20to%20meet%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20observed%20that%20the%20FIR%20itself%20indicates%20the%20woman%20was%20aware%20the%20accused%20was%20married%20and%20continued%20to%20believe%20his%20assurance%20regarding%20marriage%20despite%20this%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20is%20adult%20enough%20to%20know%20the%20law%20forbids%20a%20second%20marriage%20and%20there%20is%20no%20allegation%20in%20the%20complaint%20that%20the%20accused%20promised%20to%20divorce%20his%20first%20wife%20and%20then%20marry%20her.%20Even%20otherwise%2C%20this%20would%20purely%20be%20wishful%20thinking%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20woman%20that%20the%20accused%20will%20marry%20her%20after%20divorcing%20his%20existing%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2031%20years%2C%20there%20were%20many%20opportunities%20for%20the%20woman%20to%20break%20away%20and%20lodge%20a%20complaint%20against%20the%20accused%20but%20she%20did%20not%20do%20so%2C%20the%20bench%20noted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722528060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F4d6orptg_bombay-high-court-_625x300_14_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhc-quashes-rape-case-against-73-year-old-man-notes-relationship-of-30-years-was-consensual-6240596%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20quashed%20a%20case%20lodged%20against%20a%2073-year-old%20man%20for%20allegedly%20sexually%20abusing%20a%20woman%20since%201987%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20relationship%20was%20consensual.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhc-quashes-rape-case-against-73-year-old-man-notes-relationship-of-30-years-was-consensual-6240596%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhc-quashes-rape-case-against-73-year-old-man-notes-relationship-of-30-years-was-consensual-6240596%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhc-quashes-rape-case-against-73-year-old-man-notes-relationship-of-30-years-was-consensual-62405