20by%20IAS%20Minal%20Karanwal%2C%20has%20been%20empowering%20young%20rural%20girls.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinal%20identified%2060%20active%20gram%20panchayats%20in%20Nanded%20and%20conducted%20an%20orientation%20session.%20At%20least%20five%20young%20girls%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2011%20to%2018%20years%20in%20each%2060%20panchayats%20were%20identified%20to%20make%20a%20model%20%E2%80%98Balika%20Panchayat%E2%80%99%20that%20mimics%20a%20regular%20gram%20panchayat%20with%20five%20officeholders.%20Among%20these%2C%20one%20acts%20as%20a%20sarpanch%20(village%20head).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20slate%20was%20wide%20open%20and%20I%20asked%20them%20to%20write%20on%20it%20as%20they%20wished.%20I%20gave%20them%20a%20period%20of%20three%20months%20to%20implement%20the%20project%20on%20ground%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConsidering%20their%20broad%20objective%2C%20they%20took%20most%20initiatives%20such%20as%20organising%20cleanliness%20drives%20in%20the%20village%2C%20getting%20the%20numbers%20and%20names%20fixed%20up%20on%20the%20members%20in%20the%20gram%20panchayats%2C%20organising%20meetings%20(gram%20sabhas)%2C%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20girls%20started%20an%20entire%20campaign%20for%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F18554%2Fone-man-turned-village-alcohol-tobacco-free-zone%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20alcohol%20ban%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20villages.%20For%20this%2C%20they%20went%20door-to-door%20to%20motivate%20people%20and%20explain%20the%20ill-effects%20of%20consuming%20liquor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20her%20experience%20of%20conducting%20such%20a%20campaign%2C%20Mahadevi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20would%20come%20home%20drunk%20and%20cause%20trouble%20for%20members%20in%20their%20homes.%20When%20young%20girls%20explained%20how%20their%20habit%20had%20been