0too%20many%20shops%2C%20too%20many%20bright%20lights%2C%20aromatic%20smells%3B%20all%20my%20senses%20get%20so%20distracted%20with%20so%20many%20things%20in%20my%20surroundings.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Stimming%20makes%20us%20feel%20comfortable%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShort%20for%20self-stimulating%20behaviour%20%E2%80%94%20stimming%20refers%20to%20doing%20an%20action%20over%20and%20over%20or%20repeating%20the%20same%20sound%20several%20times.%20A%20coping%20mechanism%20is%20how%2018-year-old%20Aarav%20Krishnatheeram%20describes%20it%20to%20be.%20Life%20is%20tough%20without%20it%2C%20he%20notes.%20While%20for%20Aarav%2C%20the%20stimming%20involves%20actions%20like%20shouting%20and%20rocking%20himself%2C%20for%20Navneet%20it%20means%20moving%20his%20fingers%20up%20and%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20my%20behaviour%20may%20look%20funny%20to%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20provides%20him%20recourse%20when%20he%20is%20in%20a%20high-activity%20zone.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20go%20out%2C%20all%20the%20surroundings%20distract%20my%20vision%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20my%20body%20is%20flying%20and%20my%20head%20is%20banging.%20To%20balance%20my%20sensory%20system%20I%20do%20stimming.%20I%20feel%20safe%20and%20comfortable%20when%20I%20fidget%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20treat%20us%20like%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20exist%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Chitra%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Tarun%20Paul%20Mathew%20(17)%2C%20the%20saddest%20reality%20is%20losing%20one%E2%80%99s%20identity.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20true%20for%20many%20of%20us%20non-speaking%20autistics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%20But%20writing%2C%20he%20says%2C%20has%20helped%20position%20him%20and%20other%20neurodivergent%20individuals%20(who%20are%20unable%20to%20communicate%20through%20speech)%20on%20the%20same%20