ter-collegiate%20sports.%20However%2C%20sports%20took%20a%20backseat%20after%20life%20and%20different%20priorities%20took%20over%20post%20marriage.%20One%20thing%20that%20remained%20constant%20throughout%20her%20life%20though%20was%20going%20to%20her%20gym.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turning%20point%20that%20transformed%20this%20mother%20of%20two%20into%20a%20champion%20was%20the%20inauguration%20of%20a%20swimming%20pool%20in%202011.%20Ever%20ready%20for%20a%20challenge%2C%20Ranjita%2C%20who%20was%20then%20in%20her%20late%2040s%2C%20dove%20into%20the%20pool%2C%20which%20for%20her%2C%20brimmed%20with%20possibilities.%20Soon%2C%20she%20started%20competing%20in%20district%2C%20state%2C%20national%20and%20international%20level%20competitions%2C%20emerging%20victorious%20each%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntranced%20by%20the%20world%20of%20competitive%20sports%2C%20she%20then%20tried%20her%20hand%20at%20powerlifting%20and%20arm%20wrestling%20too.%20The%20result%20%E2%80%94%20just%20as%20you%20expected%20%E2%80%94%20earned%20her%20the%20title%20of%20%E2%80%98Iron%20Lady%20of%20Assam%E2%80%99%20at%20the%20state%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20incredibly%20proud%20of%20her.%20I%20remember%20the%20first%20time%20she%20won%20a%20competition%20in%20swimming.%20It%20was%20sometime%20in%202013-14%20and%20we%20threw%20a%20big%20party%20for%20her%20with%20all%20relatives%20and%20friends.%20They%20all%20were%20so%20proud%20of%20her%20and%20wanted%20her%20to%20continue%20and%20achieve%20bigger%20things.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20happiest%20I%20had%20ever%20seen%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20her%20son%20Anjumon%2C%20his%20voice%20brimming%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%E2%80%99ve%20always%20heard%20parents%20speak%20about%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20achievements.%20It%E2%80%99s%20pleasantly%20surprising%20when%20the%20tables%20are%20turned%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%2062-year-old%20Ranjita%E2%80%99s%20inspiring%20tale%20of%20achieving%20her%20dreams%2C%20age%20no%20bar!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20down%20a%20government%20job%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20a%20Bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20(BSc)%20in%20agriculture%2C%20Ranjita%20got%20a%20government%20job.%20Post%20marriage%2C%20she%20shifted%20to%20a%20nearby%20district%20of%20Jorhat%2C%20where%20she%20continued%20her%20service.%20She%20then%20moved%20to%20the%20Philippines%20for%20a%20few%20years%20for%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20PhD%20degree.%20Always%20eager%20to%20learn%2C%20she%20pursued%20a%20course%20in%20computer%20programming%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6mYkQLhNDG%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6mYkQLhNDG%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6mYkQLhNDG%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Ranjita%20Phukan%20Gogoi%20(%40ranjitaphukangogoi)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20couple%20was%20often%20invited%20to%20pool%20parties.%20While%20everyone%20swam%20around%20and%20had%20a%20gala%20time%2C%20including%20Mr%20Gogoi%2C%20the%20Mrs%20had%20to%20use%20a%20float.%20This%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20burning%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332716%2Fjanaki-amma-swimming-lessons-for-women-kids-reduce-drowning-deaths-in-kerala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesire%20to%20learn%20swimming%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20almost%20like%20an%20inferiority%20complex.%20While%20everyone%20enjoyed%20themselves%2C%20I%20was%20stuck%20in%20the%20sidelines.%20Couples%20swam%20together%20while%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20join%20my%20husband%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ranjita%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20in%20the%20early%2090s%20and%20after%20they%20returned%20to%20India%2C%20the%20swimming%20dream%20remained%20unfulfilled%20as%20there%20was%20no%20swimming%20pool%20nearby.%20By%20the%20time%2C%20their%20family%20too%20had%20grown%20and%20Ranjita%20juggled%20motherhood%20with%20her%20job.%20However%2C%20she%20had%20to%20quit%20in%20a%20few%20years%2C%20a%20regret%20which%20haunts%20Anjumon%20till%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20in%20nursery%20school%20and%20would%20miss%20my%20mom%20after%20coming%20back%20home.%20I%20would%20cry%20and%20tell%20her%20to%20be%20at%20home%20due%20to%20which%20she%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20never%20joined%20back.%20I%20regret%20it%20even%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjita%20kept%20herself%20busy%20tending%20to%20her%20beautiful%20garden%2C%20a%20hobby%20that%20she%20continues%20even%20today%20amidst%20her%20hectic%20schedule.%20She%20was%20soon%20kept%20busier%20by%20another%20addition%20to%20the%20family%2C%20Anjumon%E2%80%99s%20brother.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%