20is%20reminiscent%20of%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20abode.%20Creating%20the%2015-ft%20doppelganger%20homestay%2C%20the%20brothers%20say%2C%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20goal%20that%20backed%20their%20transition%20from%20their%20city%20life%20in%20Delhi%20to%20the%20mountains%20in%202021.%20Instead%2C%20it%20was%20a%20consequence%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20architects%2C%20Raghav%20and%20Ansh%20(27)%20were%20keen%20on%20living%20an%20%E2%80%9Cintentional%20life%20closer%20to%20nature%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dream%20they%20felt%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20achieved%20by%20being%20a%20part%20of%20modern%20corporate%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F247572%2Fmaharashtra-ecofriendly-green-architecture-domes-arches-cost-effective-sustainable-homes-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchitectural%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20prized%20demand%20over%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20disconnect%20between%20the%20architect%20and%20the%20labour%20involved%20in%20these%20projects.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20greenwashing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raghav%20notes.%20Prior%20to%202021%2C%20the%20Delhi-based%20boys%20had%20their%20week%20cut%20out%20for%20them%20%E2%80%94%20weekdays%20spent%20working%20long%20hours%20and%20weekends%20trekking%20to%20North%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F9_3aPdHLQ9Y%3Fsi%3DuSBCfoXQnBlYuCgm%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seed%20for%20Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%20was%20sown%20when%2C%20after%20one%20particular%20trek%20to%20Rishikesh%20in%20December%202020%2C%20Raghav%20and%20Ansh%20found%20themselves%20wishing%20they%20could%20stay%20back%20in%20the%20mountains%20and%20not%20return%20to%20the%20monotonous%20hustle.%20And%20they%20decided%20to%20do%20just%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20completely%20bewildered%20by%20topics%20of%20gardening%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F189744%2Fbangalore-lifestyle-one-day-holiday-village-rural-pottery-green-trip-village-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20rural%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20journey%20of%20building%20Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%20has%20stretched%20their%20understanding%20in%20these%20regards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%20invite%20us%20into%20their%20home.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%20is%20a%20sustainably%20built%20homestay%20in%20Rishikesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358212%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETiny%20Farm%20Fort%20is%20a%20sustainably%20built%20homestay%20in%20Rishikesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Atik%20Bheda%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3