oads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-3-1722003070-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358796%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETrainees%20at%20an%20L%26amp%3BT%20CSTI%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDev%20Kumar%20Bera%20has%20been%20working%20at%20a%20Tata%20Steel%20plant%20as%20a%20scaffolding%20supervisor%20for%201.5%20years%20after%20undergoing%20training%20at%20the%20CSTI%20in%20Kolkata.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20gained%20a%20lot%20of%20respect%20after%20enrolling%20in%20the%20programme.%20It%20has%20completely%20turned%20around%20our%20fortunes.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20celebrate%20my%20sister%E2%80%99s%20marriage%20and%20prove%20the%20villagers%20who%20mocked%20me%2C%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20with%20an%20unmissable%20hint%20of%20pride%20in%20his%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20CSTIs%20have%20turned%20around%20the%20lives%20of%20thousands%20of%20young%20Indians%20like%20Dev%2C%20proving%20the%20impact%20of%20skills%20training.%20L%26amp%3BT%20is%20not%20only%20aiding%20in%20their%20personal%20growth%20but%20also%20contributing%20robustly%20to%20the%20national%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20some%20other%20skill-building%20initiatives%20of%20L%26amp%3BT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESkill%20Trainers%20Academy%20(STA)%3A%20It%20focuses%20on%20training%20trainers%20and%20offers%20programmes%20in%20sectors%20like%20BFSI%2C%20capital%20goods%2C%20construction%2C%20electronics%2C%20and%20management%20and%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EProject%20Neev%3A%20This%20initiative%20helps%20disabled%20people%20become%20self-reliant%20through%20job%20skill%20training.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EVocational%20training%20for%20women%3A%20Women%20from%20low-income%20groups%20are%20provided%20with%20training%20in%20tailoring%2C%20beautician%20skills%2C%20home%20nursing%2C%20and%20food%20processing.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20forward%2C%20the%20engineering%20giant%20plans%20to%20expand%20its%20network%20of%20training%20centres%20to%20reach%20as%20many%20rural%20youth%20as%20possible.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20plans%20to%20introduce%20a%20range%20of%20courses%20that%20closely%20align%20with%20current%20industry%20requirements%20while%20enhancing%20partnerships%20with%20key%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20in%20partnership%20with%20L%26amp%3BT.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722051000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-1722002541.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358777%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20(L%26amp%3BT)%E2%80%99s%20Construction%20Skills%20Training%20Institutes%20(CSTIs)%20provide%20vocational%20training%20to%20underprivileged%20rural%20youth%2C%20equipping%20them%20with%20essential%20skills%20for%20the%20construction%20sector.%20These%20institutes%20have%20helped%20many%20secure%20employment%20with%20top%20construction%20companies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A232%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98My%20Disability%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Limit%20My%20Service%E2%80%99%3A%20Visually-Impaired%20Civil%20Servant%20On%20UPSC%20Disability%20Quota%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20surrounding%20the%20selection%20of%20Puja%20Khedkar%2C%20the%20trainee%20IAS%20(Indian%20Administrative%20Service)%20officer%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20cadre%2C%20who%20allegedly%20availed%20of%20concessions%20for%20physical%20disability%20and%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes%20reservations)%2C%20has%20sparked%20a%20furious%20debate%20online%20on%20reservations%20for%20the%20disabled%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20elite%20civil%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20various%20revelations%20of%20alleged%20impropriety%20in%20the%20media%2C%20her%20two-year%20training%20has%20been%20put%20on%20hold%2C%20and%20her%20selection%20into%20the%20IAS%20is%20now%20being%20probed%20by%20a%20panel%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Union%20Government.%20What%20this%20decision%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20done%20is%20lessen%20the%20volume%20of%20those%20questioning%20the%20need%20for%20a%20disability%20quota%20in%20the%20elite%20civil%20services%20given%20their%20concerns%20of%20%E2%80%98misuse%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Constitution%20guarantees%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341616%2Fbest-books-on-disability-inclusivity-mental-health-stigma-sign-language-books%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eequal%20rights%20and%20opportunities%20for%20the%20disabled%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recognising%20those%20persons%20with%2040%25%20or%20more%20disability%20certified%20by%20medical%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20everything%20from%20hearing%20impairment%20to%20visual%20impairment%2C%20blindness%2C%20and%20locomotive%20disabilities.%20Under%20the%20Disability%20Discrimination%20Act%2C%201995%2C%20a%203%25%20reservation%20is%20provided%20for%20the%20disabled.%20This%20law%20was%20replaced%20by%20the%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%2C%202016%2C%20which%20increases%20reservations%20to%204%25%20for%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(PwD)%20in%20various%20sectors%2C%20including%20those%20attempting%20the%20UPSC%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20(CSE).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20senior%20IAS%20officer%20of%20Telangana%20cadre%2C%20Smita%20Sabharwal%2C%20wrote%20a%20post%20on%20X%20questioning%20the%20provision%20of%20reservations%20for%20disabled%20persons%20in%20the%20civil%20services.%20She%20posed%20on%20X%3A%20%E2%80%9CWith%20all%20due%20respect%20to%20the%20Differently%20Abled.%20Does%20an%20Airline%20hire%20a%20pilot%20with%20%5Ba%5D%20disability%3F%20Or%20would%20you%20trust%20a%20surgeon%20with%20a%20disability.%20The%20nature%20of%20the%20%23AIS%20(IAS%2FIPS%2FIFoS)%20is%20field-work%2C%20long%20taxing%20hours%2C%20listening%20first%20hand%20to%20people%E2%80%99s%20grievances-which%20requires%20physical%20fitness.%20Why%20does%20this%20premier%20service%20need%20this%20Quota%20in%20the%20first%20place!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20Amitabh%20Kant%2C%20an%20ex-civil%20servant%20and%20former%20CEO%20of%20NITI%20Aayog%2C%20sought%20a%20review%20of%20the%20disability%20quota.%20He%20posted%20on%20X%3A%20%E2%80%9CSeveral%20cases%20of%20fraud%20through%20UPSC%20for%20entry%20to%20top%20Civil%20Services%20are%20being%20alleged.%20All%20such%20cases%20must%20be%20fully%20investigated%20and%20the%20sternest%20action%20taken.%20Selection%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20competence%20and%20integrity%20should%20never%20get%20compromised.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20in%20favour%20of%20SC%2FST%20and%20OBC%20reservation.%20These%20reservations%20should%20continue%2C%20with%20the%20Creamy%20layer%20regulations%20being%20enforced.%20However%2C%20the%20existing%20reservations%20for%20the%20physically%20and%20mentally%20handicapped%20and%20the%20proposed%201%25%20reservations%20for%20the%20third%20gender%20for%20the%20top%20Civil%20Services%20need%20to%20be%20reviewed.%20They%20are%20being%20misused%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20a%20trustee%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fncpedp_india%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ncpedp_india%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20see%20thousands%20of%20innovative%20outcomes%20by%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20which%20is%20inspirational%20in%20many%20ways.%20NCPEDP%20was%20instrumental%20in%20getting%20disabled%20people%20in%20UPSC%20%26amp%3B%20we%20see%20them%20struggling%20daily%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20awareness.%20If%20given%20a%20universal%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FM6TUgDSIUY%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FM6TUgDSIUY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Arvind%20Gupta%20(%40buzzindelhi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbuzzindelhi%2Fstatus%2F1814941451001999420%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20need%20disability%20quota%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F178902%2Fupsc-result-topper-tips-farmer-son-ias-inspiring-india%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESatender%20Singh%20Pannu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20visually-impaired%20civil%20servant%20who%20is%20currently%20undergoing%20training%20at%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Training%20(Union%20Territories%20Civil%20Services)%2C%20says%20that%20the%20arguments%20that%20question%20the%20need%20for%20a%20disability%20quota%20are%20misplaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20opinions%2C%20he%20argues%2C%20have%20four%20profoundly%20disturbing%20problems%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20They%E2%80%99re%20ableist%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20denial%20of%20enabling%20conditions%20and%20affirmative%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20These%20views%20go%20against%20constitutional%20guarantees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4)%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20denial%20of%20social%20justice%20and%20the%20principle%20of%20reasonable%20accommodation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20first%20point%2C%20Satender%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20opinions%20exhibit%20an%20ableist%20point%20of%20view%2C%20which%20believes%20that%20people%20with%20disability%20are%20incompetent%20and%20incapable%20of%20performing%20the%20tasks%20that%20they%20are%20supposed%20to%20perform%20as%20IAS%20officers.%20But%20there%20are%20civil%20servants%20availing%20of%20the%20disability%20quota%20who%20have%20done%20better%20than%20their%20%E2%80%98able-bodied%E2%80%99%20peers%20in%20their%20various%20revenue%20postings.%20As%20DMs%20or%20SDMs%2C%20they%20have%20shown%20to%20be%20more%20than%20capable%20of%20going%20on%20field%20visits%2C%20listening%20to%20public%20grievances%20and%20fulfilling%20all%20other%20tasks%20expected%20of%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20his%20own%20experience%2C%20Satender%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CAffirmative%20action%20has%20definitely%20acted%20as%20an%20enabler.%20As%20a%20civil%20servant%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20in%20different%20roles.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20perception%20that%20a%20person%20with%20a%20visual%20disability%20will%20struggle%20to%20work%20as%20an%20effective%20officer%2C%20which%20is%20absolutely%20untrue.%20Seldom%20do%20people%20know%20the%20role%20of%20technology%20like%20screen%20reading%20software%2C%20text-to-speech%20technologies%2C%20and%20text%20reading%20technologies%2C%20which%20can%20even%20read%20handwriting%2C%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20to%20assist%20officers%20like%20us.%20These%20technologies%20and%20my%20own%20slight%20adjustments%20and%20adaptations%20have%20ensured%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20as%20competent%20as%20anybody%20else.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20second%20point%2C%20he%20also%20believes%20that%20such%20arguments%20also%20reflect%20the%20denial%20of%20enabling%20conditions%20and%20the%20project%20of%20social%20inclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDisability%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20stamina%20or%20competence.%20For%20people%20from%20excluded%20communities%2C%20what%20matters%20is%20the%20provision%20of%20conditions%20that%20will%20enable%20them%20to%20thrive.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295507%2Fdisability-inclusive-policy-at-workplaces-lessons-from-accenture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWe%20need%20enabling%20conditions%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20overcome%20caste%2C%20class%20and%20other%20such%20social%20constructs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20strive%20to%20eradicate%20caste%20through%20affirmative%20action.%20Similarly%2C%20we%20need%20enabling%20conditions%20for%20the%20disabled%20so%20that%20society%20can%20step%20out%20of%20its%20ableist%20mentality.%20They%20should%20not%20be%20excluded%20from%20service%20just%20because%20they%20happen%20to%20be%20victims%20of%20social%20structures%2C%20prejudicial%20benefits%20and%20inaccessible%20attitudes.%20We%20need%20to%20be%20provided%20with%20attitudinal%2C%20structural%20and%20institutional%20accessibility%20for%20us%20to%20perform%20our%20role%20as%20officers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-2-1722004219.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22UPSC%20exam%20gives%20disability%20quota%20for%20IAS%20officers%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-2-1722004219.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-2-1722004219-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-2-1722004219-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-2-1722004219-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-2-1722004219-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358813%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Disability%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20stamina%20or%20competence%E2%80%99%20(For%20representational%20purposes%20only)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatender%20also%20believes%20that%20the%20real%20issue%20is%20being%20lost%20amidst%20all%20the%20noise%20surrounding%20the%20Puja%20Khedkar%20controversy.%20As%20he%20argues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20distraction%20from%20the%20real%20issue.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20about%20scrapping%20affirmative%20action%20for%20the%20disabled.%20The%20real%20issue%20is%20to%20implement%20it%20properly.%20Reservation%20has%20not%20been%20implemented%20in%20its%20true%20spirit%2C%20and%20now%20we%20have%20forgery%2C%20deception%20and%20fake%20certificates%20that%20eat%20into%20it.%20This%20should%20be%20talked%20about%20and%20rectified.%20We%20should%20not%20throw%20the%20baby%20out%20with%20the%20bathwater.%20Everyone%20deserves%20a%20chance%20to%20live%20with%20dignity%2C%20including%20a%20disabled%20person%2C%20and%20this%20is%20their%20constitutional%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20committed%20to%20providing%20the%20disabled%20with%20all%20the%20rights%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(RPWD)%20Act%2C%202016%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Convention%20on%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(UNCRPD)%2C%20and%20other%20such%20covenants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20should%20exclude%20someone%20from%20a%20responsibility%20they%E2%80%99re%20competent%20to%20execute%20if%20they%20satisfy%20all%20the%20required%20conditions.%20People%20who%20have%20availed%20of%20the%20disability%20quota%20have%20cleared%20the%20civil%20service%20examinations%20(CSE).%20They%20have%20cleared%20the%20same%20exam%20as%20able-bodied%20people%20who%20are%20talking%20about%20scrapping%20reservations%20for%20the%20elite%20service.%20Scrapping%20something%20like%20the%20disability%20quota%20goes%20against%20their%20rights%2C%20dignity%2C%20and%20social%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20on%20the%20fourth%20point%2C%20Satender%20argues%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20note%20that%20we%20have%20already%20identified%20services%20in%20which%20people%20with%20disabilities%20can%20perform%20well%2C%20and%20the%20IAS%20is%20one%20of%20them.%20This%20has%20been%20done%20following%20the%20principle%20of%20reasonable%20accommodation.%20We%20have%20not%20identified%20flying%20an%20aeroplane%20or%20the%20responsibility%20of%20an%20IPS%20officer%20for%20the%20visually%20impaired.%20The%20roles%20that%20have%20already%20been%20identified%20and%20considered%20suitable%20for%20visually%20impaired%20persons%20should%20not%20be%20denied%20to%20them%2C%20in%20which%20they%20have%20already%20established%20themselves.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDo%20we%20need%20a%20review%20of%20the%20disability%20quota%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatender%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20that%20we%20need%20to%20review%20the%20reservation%20quota%20for%20the%20disabled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20because%20some%20facility%20is%20being%20encroached%20upon%2C%20you%20do%20not%20end%20it.%20You%20punish%20the%20encroachers%20and%20proactively%20plug%20the%20loopholes%20to%20allow%20genuine%20candidates%20to%20use%20the%20facility.%20Reservation%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%20needs%20to%20be%20implemented%20in%20its%20true%20spirit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20former%20decorated%20IAS%20officer%20who%20also%20availed%20of%20the%20disability%20quota%20but%20wishes%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20actually%20shocked%20that%20she%20%5BPuja%20Khedkar%5D%20could%20bypass%20all%20the%20checks.%20I%20am%20actually%20puzzled%20how%20these%20people%20can%20actually%20get%20through%20it.%20The%20vetting%20process%20for%20candidates%20availing%20the%20disability%20quota%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20stringent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20720px)%20100vw%2C%20720px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFB_IMG_1722001043015-1722003789.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Disability%20Quota%20UPSC%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFB_IMG_1722001043015-1722003789.jpg%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFB_IMG_1722001043015-1722003789-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFB_IMG_1722001043015-1722003789-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFB_IMG_1722001043015-1722003789-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFB_IMG_1722001043015-1722003789-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358806%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESatender%20Singh%20(on%20the%20Right)%20with%20the%20Union%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20cannot%20question%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20quota.%20It%20should%20remain%20to%20ensure%20that%20disabled%20people%20are%20brought%20into%20the%20mainstream%20of%20the%20Indian%20bureaucracy.%20But%20the%20way%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20implemented%20needs%20to%20change%20and%20this%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20require%20earth-shattering%20reforms.%20All%20you%20have%20to%20do%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20people%20who%20are%20there%20conducting%20this%20examination%20are%20held%20accountable.%20What%20we%20need%20here%20is%20simple%20tweaks%20and%20basic%20accountability.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20difficult%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBarriers%20to%20entry%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20all%20the%20noise%2C%20a%20major%20issue%20that%20is%20being%20missed%20is%20the%20denial%20of%20opportunities%20to%20disabled%20candidates%20who%20have%20cleared%20the%20exam%20but%20are%20either%20inducted%20into%20a%20service%20that%20they%20haven%E2%80%99t%20sought%20or%20not%20inducted%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20the%20example%20of%202003-batch%20IAS%20officers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F162571%2Frigzin-samphel-ias-ladakh-uttar-pradesh-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERigzin%20Samphel%3C%2Fa%3E%20(UP%20cadre)%20and%20DS%20Lokesh%20Kumar%20(Telangana%20cadre)%20who%20had%20to%20file%20a%20case%20in%20a%20court%20before%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20(PMO)%20intervened%20on%20their%20behalf%20to%20get%20their%20preferred%20service%20(IAS)%20allotted%20to%20them.%20Samphel%2C%20a%202003-batch%20officer%20with%20All%20India%20Rank%20(AIR)%20120%20and%20AIR%202%20(Scheduled%20Tribe)%2C%20was%20also%20eligible%20for%20the%20disability%20quota%20(locomotor)%20given%20his%20severely%20damaged%20right%20leg.%20Lokesh%20was%20eligible%20for%20the%20same%20quota%20after%20contracting%20polio%20on%20one%20leg%20at%20a%20young%20age.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20virtue%20of%20being%20an%20ST%20(Scheduled%20Tribe)%20candidate%2C%20Samphel%20should%20have%20been%20given%20the%20IAS%20since%20that%20year%20there%20were%20six%20seats%20available%20for%20ST%20category%20candidates.%20Even%20if%20he%20was%20denied%20all%20reservation%20quotas%2C%20the%20Government%20should%20have%20inducted%20him%20into%20the%20IRS%20since%20he%20had%20finished%20AIR%20120%20(General%20category).%20Instead%2C%20he%20was%20allotted%20the%20Indian%20Information%20Service%20(IIS)%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20(DoPT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20(DoPT)%20reasoning%20was%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20promote%20disabled%20people%20in%20the%20services%2C%20and%20there%20were%20seats%20specifically%20reserved%20for%20them%20in%20the%20IIS%20but%20not%20the%20IAS.%20In%20response%2C%20Samphel%20and%20Lokesh%20told%20the%20DoPT%20that%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20reservation%20under%20the%20disability%20quota%20and%20that%20they%20should%20have%20been%20allocated%20the%20IAS%20by%20virtue%20of%20their%20performance%20in%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-1722004133.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Disability%20quota%20in%20the%20IAS%20via%20the%20UPSC%20exam%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-1722004133.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-1722004133-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-1722004133-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-1722004133-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-1722004133-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358811%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20representational%20purposes%20only%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELokesh%2C%20AIR%20122%20and%20AIR%206%20(Scheduled%20Caste)%2C%20was%20eligible%20for%20IAS%20since%20that%20year%2C%20there%20were%20eight%20seats%20available%20for%20SC%20category%20candidates.%20Hurt%20by%20this%20injustice%2C%20Samphel%20and%20Lokesh%20filed%20a%20case%20in%202003%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20saying%20they%20did%20not%20want%20the%20benefit%20of%20reservation%20under%20the%20disability%20quota%20because%20it%20was%20being%20used%20against%20their%20interest.%20By%20virtue%20of%20their%20own%20merit%2C%20they%20were%20getting%20into%20the%20service%20of%20their%20choice%20(IAS)%2C%20but%20the%20rules%20listed%20in%20the%20Disability%20Act%2C%201995%2C%20were%20being%20used%20in%20an%20%E2%80%98illogical%20manner%E2%80%99%20to%20deny%20them%20entry%20into%20the%20IAS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20their%20case%2C%20however%2C%20there%20was%20a%20separate%20PIL%20(public%20interest%20litigation)%20filed%20by%20two%20judges%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20who%20happened%20to%20read%20about%20their%20case%20in%20the%20media.%20Concurrently%2C%20Samphel%20and%20Lokesh%20went%20about%20pursuing%20their%20own%20case%20through%20the%20then%20Ladakh%20MP%20Thupstan%20Chhewang%20and%20they%20approached%20the%20PMO%20for%20their%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20luck%20would%20have%20it%2C%20the%20PMO%20was%20benevolent%20towards%20their%20cause%20and%20ordered%20a%20second%20medical%20examination%20to%20see%20whether%20they%20were%20fit%20to%20serve%20in%20the%20IAS%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DoPT%20reconstituted%20a%20medical%20board%20in%202004%20to%20assess%20whether%20they%20were%20capable%20of%20carrying%20out%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20IAS%20in%20terms%20of%20physical%20fitness.%20After%20putting%20Samphel%20and%20Lokesh%20through%20various%20tests%2C%20they%20decided%20that%20both%20of%20them%20were%20fit%20for%20all%20non-technical%20services%20and%20therefore%20should%20be%20inducted%20into%20the%20IAS.%20From%20the%20time%20they%20had%20filed%20the%20case%20till%20its%20resolution%2C%20they%20were%20serving%20as%20probationers%20in%20the%20IIS%2C%20partially%20under%20duress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20resolution%2C%20there%20was%20another%20PIL%20filed%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20as%20stated%20earlier.%20This%20PIL%20snowballed%20into%20many%20questions%20from%20the%20court%20about%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20position%20on%20disabled%20candidates%20serving%20in%20the%20elite%20services.%20Finally%2C%20in%202005%2C%20the%20DoPT%20issued%20a%20circular%20saying%20that%20seats%20would%20be%20reserved%20for%20disabled%20people%20in%20the%20IAS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Samphel%20and%20Lokesh%20have%20built%20stellar%20careers%20in%20the%20service%20with%20the%20former%20taking%20voluntary%20retirement%20last%20year.%20Their%20%E2%80%98disability%E2%80%99%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20their%20ability%20to%20serve.%20Despite%20the%20examples%20they%E2%80%99ve%20set%2C%20the%20system%20seems%20determined%20to%20keep%20deserving%20disabled%20candidates%20out%20of%20the%20higher%20echelons%20of%20the%20Indian%20bureaucracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20must%20read%20inspiring%20journey%20of%20a%20differently-abled%20IAS%20officer%20of%20Telangana%20cadre%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20the%20year%202003%2C%20a%20UPSC%20AIS%20aspirant%20worked%20hard%20%26amp%3B%20secured%20a%20good%20rank%20.%20But%20instead%20of%20IAS%20posting%2C%20he%20was%20given%20IIS%20posting%20because%20of%20his%20disability.%20There%20were%202others%20along%20with%20him%2C%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5O6iUPzO1K%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F5O6iUPzO1K%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Naveena%20(%40TheNaveena)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheNaveena%2Fstatus%2F1815690240603893924%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20the%20example%20of%20Ira%20Singhal%2C%20a%202015-batch%20IAS%20officer%20with%20hyperkyphosis%20scoliosis%2C%20a%20spine-related%20disorder%2C%20who%20topped%20the%20civil%20service%20examinations%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20prior%20to%20this%20phenomenal%20achievement%2C%20she%20had%20scored%20enough%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20IRS%2C%20but%20her%20appointment%20was%20cancelled%20with%20the%20Government%20citing%20her%20disability%20as%20a%20reason.%20She%20then%20sought%20legal%20intervention%20from%20the%20Central%20Administrative%20Tribunal%20(CAT).%20Just%20as%20she%20was%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20appearing%20for%20her%20second%20attempt%2C%20she%20received%20her%20letter%20of%20appointment%20but%20still%20went%20ahead%20with%20writing%20the%20exam%20and%20came%20back%20much%20stronger%2C%20according%20to%20an%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20you%20have%20the%20case%20of%20ISRO%20scientist%20Kartik%20Kansal%2C%20who%20suffers%20from%20muscular%20dystrophy%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20has%20been%20confined%20to%20a%20wheelchair%20since%20he%20was%2014.%20Despite%20clearing%20the%20UPSC%20exam%20four%20times%2C%20he%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20allocated%20a%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Masterminds%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%20far%2C%20Kartik%20has%20made%20a%20total%20of%20six%20attempts%20at%20the%20UPSC%20exam%2C%20successfully%20clearing%20it%20four%20times.%20His%20All%20India%20Rank%20(AIR)%20was%20813%20in%202019%2C%20improved%20to%20271%20in%202021%20(his%20best%20rank%20so%20far)%2C%20followed%20by%20784%20in%20UPSC-2022%2C%20and%20829%20in%20UPSC-2023.%20Despite%20these%20achievements%2C%20he%20has%20not%20been%20allocated%20a%20service%20in%20three%20of%20his%20successful%20attempts%2C%20and%20for%20the%20fourth%20attempt%20in%202023%2C%20service%20allocation%20is%20pending.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20case%20is%20currently%20pending%20before%20CAT%20based%20on%20his%202021%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%20DoPT%2C%20the%20%5B2021%5D%20notification%20specifies%20muscular%20dystrophy%20as%20an%20eligible%20condition%20for%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20in%20the%20IRS%20service%20category.%20However%2C%20Kartik%E2%80%99s%20condition%2C%20affecting%20both%20legs%20and%20both%20arms%20(known%20as%20Primary%20Lateral%20Sclerosis%20or%20PLS)%2C%20is%20categorised%20differently%20and%20is%20recognised%20under%20IAS%20but%20not%20under%20IRS%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20the%20DoPT%20argues%20that%20since%20the%20IRS%20does%20not%20include%20a%20category%20specifically%20for%20both%20legs%20and%20both%20arms%20disability%2C%20Kartik%20cannot%20be%20allocated%20this%20service%20despite%20his%20qualification%20under%20the%20broader%20disability%20category%20of%20muscular%20dystrophy.%20Kartik%20cannot%20be%20allotted%20the%20IRS%20service%20due%20to%20this%20mismatch%20in%20disability%20category%20specification%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKartik%20met%20all%20the%20physical%20requirements%20to%20get%20into%20the%20IRS.%20But%20he%20fell%20afoul%20of%20a%20technicality%2C%20which%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20conform%20with%20logic.%20Why%20should%20his%20condition%20be%20recognised%20under%20the%20IAS%20but%20not%20the%20IRS%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20tough%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20this%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20we%20are%20left%20with%20a%20situation%20where%20candidates%20allegedly%20engaging%20in%20forgery%20and%20deception%20are%20availing%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20disability%20quota%20whereas%20deserving%20ones%20are%20getting%20left%20out%20in%20the%20cold.%20Maybe%2C%20instead%20of%20wanting%20to%20scrap%20or%20thoroughly%20review%20the%20requirement%20for%20it%2C%20the%20system%20would%20be%20better%20placed%20to%20hold%20its%20examiners%20more%20accountable%20and%20fix%20the%20loopholes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Satender%20Singh%20and%20Shutterstock)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAdditional%20Sources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3