2%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Battling%20Bullying%20%26amp%3B%20Bias%2C%20These%20Women%20Wrestlers%E2%80%99%20Journey%20to%20Paris%20Olympics%20Is%20Forged%20in%20Grit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mahavir%20Phogat%20saw%20weightlifter%20Karnam%20Malleswari%E2%80%99s%20podium%20finish%20at%20the%202000%20Sydney%20Olympics%2C%20it%20inspired%20him%20to%20introduce%20the%20girls%20in%20his%20family%20to%20wrestling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20that%2C%20his%20aim%20was%20to%20prepare%20them%20for%20the%20Olympic%20podium.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20task%20in%20a%20state%20like%20Haryana%20with%20the%20lowest%20sex%20ratio%2C%20where%20women%E2%80%99s%20struggles%20begin%20in%20the%20womb%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20had%20been%20introduced%20in%20India%20in%20the%20mid-90s%2C%20it%20was%20largely%20confined%20to%20Delhi%20and%20had%20yet%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20Haryana.%20Mahavir%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20to%20train%20his%20daughters%20Geeta%2C%20Babita%2C%20Ritu%2C%20Sangeeta%2C%20along%20with%20his%20nieces%2C%20Vinesh%20and%20Priyanka%2C%20faced%20resistance%20from%20villagers%2C%20including%20his%20own%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20life%20inspired%20the%20Aamir%20Khan-starrer%20Bollywood%20movie%2C%20Dangal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllowing%20the%20girls%20to%20enter%20the%20mud%20pit%2C%20traditionally%20seen%20as%20a%20male%20domain%2C%20was%20met%20with%20significant%20opposition%20in%20his%20village%20Balali%20in%20Charkhi%20Dadri%20district%20(then%20in%20Bhiwani).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20almost%20a%20year-and-a-half%20later%2C%20an%20initiative%20to%20allow%20girls%20to%20train%20alongside%20boys%20at%20Chotu%20Ram%20Stadium%20Wrestling%20Centre%20in%20Rohtak%20faced%20societal%20hurdles.%20Former%20wrestlers%2C%20and%20even%20some%20coaches%2C%20expressed%20reservations%2C%20questioning%20%E2%80%9Chow%20goats%20could%20stay%20among%20the%20lions%E2%80%9D%2C%20fearing%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20girls%20would%20distract%20boys%2C%20leading%20to%20indiscipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%202024.%20What%20was%20once%20met%20with%20sarcasm%E2%80%94people%20comparing%20girls%20to%20goats%20and%20boys%20to%20lions%2C%20emphasising%20the%20perceived%20disparity%20in%20strength%20and%20prowess%20in%20the%20wrestling%20arena%E2%80%94has%20now%20become%20a%20point%20of%20pride.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%E2%80%99s%20women%20wrestlers%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20flag%20bearers%20of%20Indian%20wrestling%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20At%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Ffarmers-daughter-set-to-rock-paris-olympics-archery-shorts-parisolympics2024-sports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20Paris%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%20is%20represented%20by%20six%20wrestlers%2C%20five%20of%20whom%20are%20women%20from%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20rural%20landscape%2C%20where%20they%20once%20faced%20stiff%20opposition%20to%20entering%20the%20male-dominated%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMeet%20the%20team%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20wrestling%20contingent%20in%20Paris%20comprises%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20(50kg)%20from%20Charkhi%20Dadri%2C%20Antim%20Panghal%20(53kg)%20from%20Hisar%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263525%2Fanshu-malik-first-indian-woman-world-wrestling-championship-winner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Anshu%20Malik%20(57kg)%20from%20Jind%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nisha%20Dahiya%20(68kg)%20from%20Panipat%2C%20Reetika%20Hooda%20(76kg)%20from%20Rohtak%2C%20along%20with%20the%20lone%20male%20wrestler%2C%20Aman%20Sehrawat%20(57kg)%20from%20Jhajjar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COlympics%20is%20every%20sportsperson%E2%80%99s%20dream%2C%20and%20I%20am%20feelin